Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.06,0:00:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was being too selfish and couldn't realize how lost and confused you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.44,0:00:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not lost or confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.32,0:00:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intention of splitting up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.95,0:00:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about me, and really think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.79,0:00:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, you really need to think about what's important to you and what you should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.63,0:00:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.47,0:00:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what choice you make, I'll wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.68,0:00:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't break away from each other so easily anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.95,0:00:59.83,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Usotsuki na anata nakimushi no atashi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.83,0:01:05.79,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Doushite umaku ikanai wa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.79,0:01:11.92,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Oshare shita kami mo rain suton no tsume mo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.92,0:01:17.89,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Anata wa kidzuki mo shinai ne
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.89,0:01:25.27,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Love kanashii namida nanka ja nai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.27,0:01:29.98,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Me ga kawaite hirihiri suru dake
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.98,0:01:35.90,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kono unmei bakari I love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.82,0:01:44.79,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimi dake wo atashi dake wo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.79,0:01:49.71,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Atsui omoi wo uketomete
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.92,0:01:56.84,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Doko made mo tsunagattetai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.84,0:02:03.60,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawaikunai nakigao mo se mo aishiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.95,0:00:59.83,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't things go well between
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.83,0:01:05.79,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,the liar, you, and the crybaby, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.79,0:01:11.92,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't notice my styled hair
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.92,0:01:17.89,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,or my nice set of press-on nails.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.89,0:01:25.27,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Love isn't about the unhappy tears that go along with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.27,0:01:29.98,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Those tears only leave my eyes dry and hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.98,0:01:35.90,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,I love this destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.82,0:01:44.79,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,between only you and only me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.79,0:01:49.71,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to accept your hot feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.92,0:01:56.84,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,and be taken by you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.84,0:02:03.60,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite your uncute, tearful face and your shortness, I still love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.98,0:02:18.53,Episode title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,700)\pos(159,378)\fscx113.75\fscy103}Episode 25 ...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.23,0:02:16.28,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it still early to be looking at the exam prep books?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.28,0:02:18.74,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see the questions they've asked in previous years.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.74,0:02:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,J University... J University...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.53,0:02:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure if she hasn't decided yet, of if he still doesn't know what to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.08,0:02:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.79,0:02:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.16,0:02:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since he hasn't given me an answer yet, it probably means he's thinking about it in his own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.67,0:02:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard their English exam's really hard, so I'm kinda worried about how much I need to know...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.97,0:02:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.98,0:02:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi... if you actually get into J University, I'll respect you for the rest of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.36,0:02:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you mean you'll have the privilege of respecting me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.98,0:02:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Christmas is doomsday...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.61,0:03:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But isn't Yano moving on the 24th?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.49,0:03:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he still hasn't given you an answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.49,0:03:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.66,0:03:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost December! Will things really be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.12,0:03:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm the one who told him it's okay to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I have no choice but to believe in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.83,0:03:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, even in the worst case scenario, we'll only be apart for a year and I'm prepared for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.46,0:03:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It's only a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.47,0:03:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's not definite that Yano's going to transfer schools.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.18,0:03:26.93,Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start with your weak point, those long reading passages.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.93,0:03:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.68,0:03:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.81,0:03:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.77,0:03:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't have to apply to the College of H...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.11,0:03:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I saw your questionnaire.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.94,0:03:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trying to get into a public and national university at the same time...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.45,0:03:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be able to keep up, and you'll fail both exams--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.37,0:03:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.20,0:03:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just think about yourself, Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.16,0:03:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's both do as much we can right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.91,0:03:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.59,0:04:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.13,0:04:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano, you're not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.09,0:04:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.97,0:04:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He always... takes hold of me so tightly like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.22,0:04:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's so frustrating, but I'm going to throw myself into those collage exams!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.19,0:04:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bathroom break.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.42,0:04:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.13,0:04:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't slack off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.43,0:04:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm working on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.30,0:04:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.93,0:04:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how long a year apart from someone really is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.60,0:04:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really gotten cold all of sudden, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.98,0:05:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? It seems the same as usual to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.11,0:05:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.70,0:05:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano, why is your hand always so warm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.95,0:05:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because my heart is always so warm... huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.95,0:05:13.70,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: There's a common superstition that people with cold hands have warm hearts, and vice versa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.78,0:05:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have things backwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.33,0:05:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, why is your hand so cold, Takahashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.91,0:05:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I have a warm heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.46,0:05:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.42,0:05:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... let me take you somewhere nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.05,0:05:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other day, I found something that looks exactly like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably just another thing like this, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.06,0:05:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a puppy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.35,0:05:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought its eyes were kinda like yours, well-separated and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.40,0:05:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.02,0:05:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I catch it for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.20,0:05:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all right. You'll just waste your money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:05:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd get it on the first try.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.20,0:05:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.41,0:05:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promised...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.46,0:06:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that I would believe in Yano, no matter what answer he gave.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.92,0:06:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swore to myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.55,0:06:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that I'd support Yano.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.35,0:06:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But right now... the warmth of Yano's hand is beginning to lead me astray.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.56,0:06:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being all wishy-washy about the decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.53,0:06:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though it's understandable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.70,0:06:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a lose-lose situation always leading to regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.54,0:06:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in that case, isn't it the same whichever you pick?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.66,0:06:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.04,0:06:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The more you tease Takahashi like this, the harder it's going to be on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.25,0:06:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It may seem cruel, but if you're gonna go, just tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.68,0:06:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She normally doesn't complain very much, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.81,0:07:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And she acts appropriately to the time and place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.98,0:07:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because she knows that I only have a mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.07,0:07:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Takahashi restrains herself like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.03,0:07:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This whole thing is just weird to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.86,0:07:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom's not a little girl, but she's not really that mature either, even at forty-two.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.28,0:07:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to say "I can't leave her alone"? It's just a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.37,0:07:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she got married on her own, got divorced on her own, and decided on her new workplace all by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.54,0:07:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without caring one a bit about her son, who has entrance exams coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.75,0:07:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That one year...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.26,0:07:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why she couldn't have just waited one more year to get divorced?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.76,0:07:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like your mom asked you to go with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I supposed to pretend like I didn't feel my mom asking me to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.69,0:07:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...or hear Takahashi saying she doesn't want me to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.66,0:07:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This totally sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.57,0:08:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Takahashi's really that strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.16,0:08:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you're not just giving her time...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.33,0:08:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you don't see her beginning to regret what she said, so you're purposely delaying your decision?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.18,0:08:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Takahashi told me not to go... I might not be able to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.44,0:08:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ah, yes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.48,0:08:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna stop by the library today?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.15,0:08:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, umm... I have a student council meeting today, so go on ahead. It'll take some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.07,0:08:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.91,0:08:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.95,0:08:41.08,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H68AC68&\b1\fscx161.25\fscy81.25\frz32.067\pos(294,479)}C\Nh\Nr\Ni\Ns\Nt\Nm\Na\Ns\N \NS\Np\Ne\Nc\N{\c&H212298&}i\Na\Nl\Nt\Ny
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I should pick out a present soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.54,0:08:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Well, you'd better talk to your mother about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.43,0:09:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei... here's the day book.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.85,0:09:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.22,0:09:04.39,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H616476&\fscx187.5\fscy107.5\pos(263,214)\b1\frx2\fry8\frz35.406}Day book
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.77,0:09:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, when's the closing ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.85,0:09:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,December 24th, remember? Just like every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.19,0:09:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.78,0:09:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't received transfer papers from anyone yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.95,0:09:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I so relieved...? Wasn't I prepared for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.92,0:09:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... a whole year is a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.38,0:09:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a lot longer than I first thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.18,0:09:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.52,0:09:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It's strange of you to come over this late, Nana!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.27,0:09:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.69,0:09:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing much...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.78,0:09:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.03,0:09:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want some hot chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.61,0:09:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love some.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.53,0:09:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found a lot of potential presents for him today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lemme see, lemme see!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.78,0:10:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, this pendant! It'd really suit him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.33,0:10:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your really think so? Do you really think it's good?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.08,0:10:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They actually come in pairs, with one for a girl, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.92,0:10:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never been interested in that couple look, but I thought this might be nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.75,0:10:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can wear them every day, and we can think of each other when we're apart, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.80,0:10:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm just giving an example.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.72,0:10:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like when we're both at home or something. That whole feeling being together all day is great, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.60,0:10:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.57,0:10:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizu-chin, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.36,0:10:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.12,0:10:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.41,0:10:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I regret telling him that it's okay to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.91,0:10:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I going to do? I didn't understand a thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.84,0:10:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What it would mean for Yano to leave...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.76,0:11:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That I wouldn't be able to see him...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.51,0:11:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't imagine a world without him...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.44,0:11:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What it would mean for Yano to leave...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.57,0:11:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That I wouldn't be able to see him...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.61,0:11:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't understand a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.70,0:11:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't imagine a world without him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.87,0:11:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even if I'm finally realizing it, it's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.75,0:11:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.92,0:11:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takeuchi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.50,0:11:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're even studying here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.05,0:11:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While waiting for Yano.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.63,0:11:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa... mnemonics.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.13,0:11:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty good at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.47,0:11:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.93,0:11:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been well?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.10,0:11:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.31,0:11:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Er, have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.65,0:11:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.16,0:12:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"In order to."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.91,0:12:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.12,0:12:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still only in part two of the book, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.88,0:12:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll see in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.72,0:12:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.39,0:12:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you in shock that the school I'm trying to get into is a stretch for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.18,0:12:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't think I'm craz---
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.47,0:12:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I take back what I said the other day. I think it's perfect for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.52,0:12:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You take back what you said...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.78,0:12:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Yano. You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.41,0:12:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finished most of part two.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.79,0:12:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, gonna run to the girl's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.91,0:12:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We only went through some problems together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.42,0:12:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.71,0:13:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After you leave, though, this is probably how our time together will be spent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.32,0:13:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I take back what I said the other day. I think it's perfect for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.07,0:13:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no. Don't get distracted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.57,0:13:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if there's still time left...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.54,0:13:37.04,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&HE0BB7E&\fscx138.75\fscy120\frz328.586\pos(294,238)\frx12\fry2}Yano
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.08,0:13:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.17,0:13:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoo-hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.17,0:13:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Y-Yoo-hoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.09,0:13:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you just doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.05,0:13:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking of something stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.68,0:13:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought of something stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.51,0:13:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.06,0:13:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.10,0:13:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what time do you think it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.56,0:14:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If my parents see me, I'm toast! Let's get to the park!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.23,0:14:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.69,0:14:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shh! You're too loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.07,0:14:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How'd you get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.78,0:14:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By bus!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.49,0:14:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By bus? That last one's already left.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.33,0:14:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd he suddenly come over so late...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.33,0:14:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he... come up with his answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.53,0:14:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so mean. And after I bought you coffee, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.95,0:14:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.62,0:14:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,0:14:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't even know how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.79,0:14:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.58,0:15:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If... I were...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.51,0:15:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were to become an adult, and I had nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.89,0:15:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and I told you to pack bag and come with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.27,0:15:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's... a proposal, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.15,0:15:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.20,0:15:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.28,0:15:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You made me lose the moment, moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.75,0:15:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How old is an adult? Twenty?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.62,0:15:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.17,0:15:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you can live on your own without your parents having to look after you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.21,0:15:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be an adult soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.68,0:15:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be an adult soon, and I'll be the one doing protecting, not the one being protected.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.93,0:16:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let anyone have anything to complain about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.65,0:16:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody will be left with heart wrenching feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.56,0:16:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not my mother, not my family, not my woman. This I swear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.86,0:16:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll definitely become someone who can protect them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.29,0:16:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.29,0:16:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The lips of the one dearest to me were quivering softly in the moonlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.72,0:16:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Yano.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.81,0:16:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.47,0:16:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it was just for a second, I'm embarrassed I made such a fuss over this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.48,0:16:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's as if this winter sky was meant to test the strength of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.49,0:16:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are those feelings disrespectful of others?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.49,0:17:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to live only for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.00,0:17:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.67,0:17:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.26,0:17:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember having a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.47,0:17:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.43,0:17:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We all had a blast at Take's... and after I got a little dozy, you appeared in my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.60,0:17:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We had some problems, you got mad that you were wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.32,0:17:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and for some reason, you slapped me right in the face.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.74,0:17:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a mysterious dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.53,0:17:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.86,0:17:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.91,0:17:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you regretted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.66,0:17:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you really didn't understand anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.08,0:17:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you regretting?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.81,0:18:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I might still... make it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.15,0:18:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I might still make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.29,0:18:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was just a dream. I don't regret anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.92,0:18:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano, you weirdo! Taking your dreams so seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.68,0:18:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano, people are watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.56,0:18:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He saw straight through me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.27,0:18:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our feelings are as clear as day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.40,0:18:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We might regret this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.57,0:19:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We might never know what would've been best.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.78,0:19:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We may not know whether we're following fate or fighting it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.58,0:19:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but if we both have our wishes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.04,0:19:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, look! It's you, Nanami!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.75,0:19:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's still in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.42,0:19:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.25,0:19:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana-chaaan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.09,0:19:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.64,0:19:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Get it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.40,0:19:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.44,0:19:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My wish is for Yano's dream to come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.78,0:19:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... my wishes will become Yano's wishes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.74,0:19:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and Yano's wishes will become mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.91,0:19:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how we'll continue to support each other, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.54,0:19:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's leave what lies in our future to the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.76,0:20:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.05,0:20:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wasted all your money...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.01,0:20:05.93,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\an7\c&HBB5B6E&\fscx162.5\fscy143.75\b1\pos(407,231)}Nanami bought\N this for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.09,0:20:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were good at that game.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.06,0:20:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just used up all of my energy. Darn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.77,0:20:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.35,0:20:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... today's just pretty chilly, so my heart feels tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.82,0:20:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is snowing a lot this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.53,0:20:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... see? There goes my heart, clenching up again...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.83,0:20:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clenching up... like it's carving this moment into itself...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.92,0:20:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the sound of us walking through the snow...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.34,0:20:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like it's measuring my feelings for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.77,0:21:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dinner tonight's that stew you love.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.53,0:21:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, I'd like to get my allowance early.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.87,0:21:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to spend it on?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.58,0:21:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to spend Christmas with my girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.50,0:21:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.98,0:21:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This year's Christmas present is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.35,0:21:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tada! A full day at the Asahigawa Zoological Park!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.36,0:21:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.15,0:21:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no Disneyland, but you can go?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.53,0:21:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.57,0:21:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For... Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.79,0:21:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I'll definitely go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.83,0:21:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.83,0:21:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be able... to spend it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.79,0:22:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano's going to stay behi--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.63,0:22:02.63,cale.,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1a&10&\frz18.527\fscx131.25\fscy222.5\frx22\fry348\pos(164,155)}Available Days
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.39,0:22:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.51,0:22:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a week early, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.40,0:22:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could hear the beating of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.82,0:22:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Takahashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.25,0:22:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.50,0:22:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...with my mom to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.30,0:22:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.10,0:22:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.64,0:22:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.86,0:23:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't regret the regrettable.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.50,0:23:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I accepted that paradox...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.29,0:23:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...as this seventeen year old girl's winter began showing signs of its end.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.64,0:22:17.27,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Ima kimi ga iikaketa kotoba ga
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.27,0:22:23.78,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Yubisaki ni sotto oritekita
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.78,0:22:30.41,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanimo iwanakute ii yo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.41,0:22:36.25,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsumaida yubi wo gyutto atatamete
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.25,0:22:52.72,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotoba wa kotoba dakara kokoro hanbun mo tsutaenai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.72,0:23:05.90,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Setsunakute modokashikute yuuyake futari wo tsutsundeiru
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.90,0:23:18.12,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Komiageru mune no omoi kokoro ga itai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.09,0:23:29.43,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Moshi kimi ga tabibito ni nattara
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.43,0:23:35.89,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kore gurai kimi wo matteru darou
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.89,0:23:42.40,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kisetsu wa kawaru sono tabi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.40,0:23:48.61,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kioku ga usuragu koto ga attemo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.61,0:24:04.88,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Dareka wo konna fuu ni kokoro ippai de aisenai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.88,0:24:12.18,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Mamaritai taisetsu na kimi
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.18,0:24:18.10,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Itsu datte futari wa hitori ja nai
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.10,0:24:25.94,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kono mune ga kawaresou de
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.94,0:24:31.57,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Furete hoshii yo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.03,0:24:47.84,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Setsunakute modokashikute kaerenai kono mama aruiteitai
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.84,0:25:03.19,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Yabaisaki ni kanjiteiru kokoro no kotoba wo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.64,0:22:17.27,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,The words you were just about to say
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.27,0:22:23.78,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,fell softly onto my fingertips.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.78,0:22:30.41,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.41,0:22:36.25,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll clasp your hand tightly and warm it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.25,0:22:52.72,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Because words are words, I can't express half of the feelings in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.72,0:23:05.90,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so wrenching and irritating as the sunset engulfs the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.90,0:23:18.12,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart aches from all the feelings welling up inside of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.09,0:23:29.43,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,If you were to become a traveler,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.43,0:23:35.89,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,would I be able to wait for you as I do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.89,0:23:42.40,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,As the seasons change,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.40,0:23:48.61,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,even if our memories are to fade.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.61,0:24:04.88,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be able to love someone with all of my heart like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.88,0:24:12.18,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to protect the precious you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.18,0:24:18.10,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,The two of us are never alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.10,0:24:25.94,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Me heart feels so fragile
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.94,0:24:31.57,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,and I want you to touch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.03,0:24:47.84,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so wrenching and irritating that I can't go home. I want to keep walking like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.84,0:25:03.19,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel the words from your heart on my fingertips.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.93,0:25:35.00,Episode title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&HD46BDB&\c&HFFE1FC&\fscx91.25\fscy123.75\pos(447,375)}Final Episode Preview...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.69,0:25:08.90,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,We were all indeed here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.73,0:25:10.99,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,We lived here...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.99,0:25:13.74,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to love him...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.74,0:25:15.61,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,I loved her...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.61,0:25:20.58,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Receiving so many beginnings\N and countless feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.58,0:25:23.41,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Learning each other's\N strengths and weaknesses...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.17,0:25:32.38,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,We... were indeed here.
